    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector's dream. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and zero scratches, dings, or imperfections. Inside, the leather interior is immaculate, showing no signs of wear, and still retains that original new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect; it has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, and all scheduled maintenance is completely up to date. Every feature, from the premium infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Buyers can expect a turn-key vehicle that looks and drives like it just left the showroom floor. It has been garage-kept, smoke-free, and has a clean, accident-free history.",
